name: Human Brain Farm
summary: Zhu Zhengwei discovers that he could see the dreams of others.He quickly realizes that the human brain is as deep and boundless as the stars and the sea.Thus, he uses human brains as cloud servers to build a massive Dream World of deep consciousness and enhances his own ability.“Different from others, my dream is fixed, arguably not a dream, it's a root memory, involving the soul's core, completely documenting my past life!”“Have I... ? What I did in my dream could change the past in the genes of this body??”
author: Three Hundred Jin of Smiles
